    "body": "### Problem\n\n```\nnvim --clean --cmd \"lua require('vim._extui').enable{}\"\n```\n\nType `iabc<esc>diw<c-r>-`\n\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c112ae08-810f-4cfe-82de-ebe1a3751e6f\n\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nThe first char should be redraw.\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\n5ea6a022c02d278008fabc71970765fa282311ce\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nlinux\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nkitty",
